1148:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \brief
1149:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Starts the CSD conversion on the preconfigured sensor. This function requires
1150:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  using the CapSense_1_CSDSetupWidgetExt() function to set up the a
1151:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  widget.
