1848:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *  calibration is performed by the element with the highest sensor
1849:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *  capacitance.
1850:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *
1851:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *  Calibration fails if the achieved raw count is outside of the +/-10%
